# Task -> PR Delivery Loop

1. Select highest-priority ready task.
2. Implement smallest coherent slice.
3. Validate with project checks.
4. Update task status and evidence.
5. Prepare concise PR description focused on why and risk.

If blocked, record blocker and next action in task-engine state first; regenerate `docs/maintainers/TASKS.md` only as the human-readable view.

